snippet.title: More Proof Scarlett Johansson is Perfect Looking - Vanity Fair
snippet.description:
Go behind the scenes of our cover shoot with Captain America: The Winter Soldier, Chef, and Under the Skin star Scarlett Johansson, photographed by Craig McDean at the New York Palace Hotel.
